Summary of Ensembl identifiers for RNA-seq matrices

RNA-seq

Annotation Table

Summary of biotypes that are dropped due to low expression:

Summary of biotypes that are dropped due to merging multiple Ensembl identifiers:

Number of multi-mapped genes with NA correlation values

Many Ensembl identifiers will have total FPKM > 0, but still have many zeroes. This results in NA values in the avg.cor column for many genes where multiple Ensembl IDs map to the same gene symbol.

Note: Where ensembl_id == "Unique", correlation values are not calculated.

data.frame(
  strategy = params$strategy,
  number_of_NA = c(nrow(annot.table %>%
                          filter(ensembl_id == "Multiple",
                                 is.na(avg.cor))))
)
